snippet.title: Barn Finders - Trailer
snippet.description:
Search for valuables stashed in abandoned barns, take part in storage auctions, bid high and buy yourself a chance to find exclusive items hidden in the past.

Add Barn Finders to your Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/991170/

Stay tuned at @BarnFindersGame

by @DualityGames
